Lindsey McKeon https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lindsey_McKeon 0 Lindsey Johnson McKeon (born March 11, 1982) is an American actress. She is known for her roles as Marah Lewis on Guiding Light and Taylor James on One Tree Hill. She previously starred on Saved by the Bell: The New Class as Katie Peterson from 1996–2000.
